text: L'Horta may refer to: *Horta of Valencia, a horticultural region in Central Valencia (see also horta) and a historic comarca of the Valencian Community *Horta Nord, present-day comarca in the Valencian Community *Horta Sud, present-day comarca in the Valencian Community *Horta Oest, present-day comarca in the Valencian Community
title: L'Horta
